gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 112, Magic 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Magic, 112-107.  Kevin Durant led the way for the Suns with 31 points, 5 rebounds and 5 assists.  Bradley Beal recorded a season high 25 points on 10-13 FGs.  Paolo Banchero (28 points, nine rebounds and seven assists) and Franz Wagner (27 points, seven rebounds and six assists) combined for 55 points in the loss. The Suns improve to 17-15 on the year (9-9 at home) while the Magic move to 19-13 with the loss.
